
Overview of noun limitation

The noun limitation has 5 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (3) restriction, limitation -- (a principle that limits the extent of something; "I am willing to accept certain restrictions on my movements")
2. (3) limitation -- (the quality of being limited or restricted; "it is a good plan but it has serious limitations")
3. (1) limit, limitation -- (the greatest amount of something that is possible or allowed; "there are limits on the amount you can bet"; "it is growing rapidly with no limitation in sight")
4. limitation -- ((law) a time period after which suits cannot be brought; "statute of limitations")
5. limitation, restriction -- (an act of limiting or restricting (as by regulation))
